learning_outcomes.en:
Upon successful completion of the course:
1. Students will have learned approximately 300 new items of academic vocabulary; 2. Students will be able to recognise the most frequent Latin and Greek roots in academic vocabulary;
3. Students will be able to reflect on the vocabulary learning techniques.

learning_outcomes.et:
Kursuse lõpuks:
1. on üliõpilased omandanud umbes 300 uut akadeemilist sõna ja väljendit;
2. tunnevad üliõpilased sagedamini esinevaid võõrtüvesid;
 3. oskavad üliõpilased teadlikumalt sõnavara omandada.

description.et:
Choose the topic in the Choose tool on course's Moodle page.
<b>A successful database entry</b>
is not plagiarised (you have used your own words to get the meaning across);
is synthesised from at least three independent sources;
has a reference list of the used sources;
is coherent and logically organised;
is grammatical.
